### Detect Redundant or Conflicting Updates
Check if a variable is updated multiple times in the same function, which can introduce logic bugs or conflicting states.

```solidity
// Redundant update may introduce bugs
function stake(uint256 amount) external {
    balances[msg.sender] += amount;
    // ...
    balances[msg.sender] += amount; // duplicated update
}
```

**Invariant:** Ensure each state variable is only updated once per logical intent.
